---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'Webflow vs Durable: No-Code Powerhouse vs AI Speed',
  description: 'Webflow is powerful no-code with full design control. Durable generates complete websites in 30 seconds with AI. Webflow $14+/mo, Durable $15+/mo. Choose based on technical comfort and timeline.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['Webflow vs Durable', 'AI website builder comparison', 'Webflow review', 'Durable review', 'best website builder'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4353FF]/5 to-[#9333EA]/5 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#4353FF] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        Website Builder Comparison · 2025 Updated
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        Webflow vs Durable
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Webflow and Durable represent completely different approaches to building websites. Webflow is a powerful no-code platform with pixel-perfect control and a learning curve. Durable is an AI-powered generator that creates complete websites in 30 seconds. Webflow is for designers who want total control. Durable is for service businesses who need a site fast.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick answer: Choose Webflow if you're willing to learn and want complete design control without coding. Choose Durable if you want a functional website in seconds and don't care about custom design. Webflow takes days or weeks to master. Durable takes 30 seconds. Webflow costs $14+/month. Durable costs $15+/month. Similar price, completely different value.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- At a Glance -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Webflow vs Durable At a Glance
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold"></th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Webflow</th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Durable</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Best for</td>
            <td class="p-4">Designers, agencies, detailed control</td>
            <td class="p-4">Service businesses, beginners, speed</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Setup time</td>
            <td class="p-14">Days to weeks</td>
            <td class="p-14">30 seconds</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Learning curve</td>
            <td class="p-14">Steep (powerful but complex)</td>
            <td class="p-14">Almost none (AI does it)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Design control</td>
            <td class="p-14">Complete (pixel-perfect)</td>
            <td class="p-14">Limited (AI-generated)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">CMS</td>
            <td class="p-14">Powerful built-in CMS</td>
            <td class="p-14">No (static)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Ecommerce</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (built-in, powerful)</td>
            <td class="p-14">No (booking only)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Starting price</td>
            <td class="p-14">$14/month</td>
            <td class="p-14">$15/month</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">You own code</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (export available)</td>
            <td class="p-14">No (hosted only)</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Webflow Overview -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Webflow Does Best
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. Complete Design Control</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Webflow gives you pixel-perfect control:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Visual CSS:</strong> Every property accessible visually</li>
          <li>• <strong>Flexbox and grid:</strong> Modern layouts without code</li>
          <li>• <strong>Responsive design:</strong> Control every breakpoint</li>
          <li>• <strong>Animations:</strong> Build complex interactions visually</li>
          <li>• <strong>Custom fonts, colors, spacing:</strong> Total control over design system</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Designers who want pixel-perfect implementation without writing code.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. Powerful CMS</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Webflow's CMS is best-in-class:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Content modeling:</strong> Define your content structure</li>
          <li>• <strong>Dynamic pages:</strong> Generate pages from CMS items</li>
          <li>• <strong>Filtering and sorting:</strong> Complex queries without code</li>
          <li>• <strong>Reference fields:</strong> Connect related content</li>
          <li>• <strong>Mixed fields:</strong> Rich text, images, videos, references in one</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Blogs, portfolios, marketing sites with dynamic content.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Ecommerce Built-In</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Webflow has serious ecommerce features:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Product management:</strong> Categories, variants, digital products</li>
          <li>• <strong>Checkout customization:</strong> Design entire checkout flow</li>
          <li>• <strong>Payment integration:</strong> Stripe, PayPal built-in</li>
          <li>• <strong>Inventory tracking:</strong> Stock management</li>
          <li>• <strong>Shopping cart design:</strong> Complete visual control</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Online stores that want custom design, not template look.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Clean Code Export</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Unique advantage:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Export HTML/CSS/JS:</strong> Get actual code</li>
          <li>• <strong>Developer-friendly:</strong> Clean semantic markup</li>
          <li>• <strong>Host anywhere:</strong> Not locked to Webflow hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>WordPress export:</strong> Move to WordPress if needed</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Teams who want visual design but might need custom code later.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Durable Overview -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Durable Does Best
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. Instant Website Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Durable builds complete sites in seconds:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>30 seconds:</strong> Enter business info, get full website</li>
          <li>• <strong>Multiple pages:</strong> Home, services, about, contact generated</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI-written content:</strong> Professional copy for your industry</li>
          <li>• <strong>Service-specific:</strong> Knows what plumbers/consultants need</li>
          <li>• <strong>Customizable:</strong> Edit after generation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Service businesses who need a functional website immediately.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. Zero Technical Skills Required</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Anyone can use Durable:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>No design skills:</strong> AI handles layout</li>
          <li>• <strong>No coding:</strong> Ever</li>
          <li>• <strong>Simple editing:</strong> Click and change text/images</li>
          <li>• <strong>Hosting included:</strong> Durable handles everything</li>
          <li>• <strong>SSL included:</strong> Security built-in</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Non-technical users who want a website without learning.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Built-in Business Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Durable includes more than websites:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>CRM:</strong> Manage customers and leads</li>
          <li>• <strong>Invoicing:</strong> Create and send invoices</li>
          <li>• <strong>AI assistant:</strong> Help with business tasks</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Website traffic insights</li>
          <li>• <strong>Booking:</strong> Customers can schedule</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> Small businesses who want all-in-one platform.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. AI-First Approach</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Everything uses AI:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Conversational:</strong> Tell AI what you need</li>
          <li>• <strong>Iterative:</strong> Ask AI to refine, add, change</li>
          <li>• <strong>Smart suggestions:</strong> AI recommends improvements</li>
          <li>• <strong>Content generation:</strong> AI writes copy, descriptions</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Best for:</strong> People who want AI to do the heavy lifting.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      When to Choose Each
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Choose Webflow if:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• You're a designer or want to learn design</li>
          <li>• You need pixel-perfect custom design</li>
          <li>• You're building complex site (ecommerce, CMS)</li>
          <li>• You want to export code later</li>
          <li>• You're willing to invest time in learning</li>
          <li>• You care about animation and micro-interactions</li>
          <li>• You want full control over every element</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Choose Durable if:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• You're service business (plumber, consultant, agency)</li>
          <li>• You need website today, not next week</li>
          <li>• You don't want to learn technical skills</li>
          <li>• You want AI to generate content and design</li>
          <li>• You need CRM/invoicing built-in</li>
          <li>• You don't care about cutting-edge custom design</li>
          <li>• You want simple, functional site fast</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Feature Comparison -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Feature Comparison
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-gray-100">
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Feature</th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Webflow</th>
            <th class="text-left p-4 font-bold">Durable</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Setup time</td>
            <td class="p-14">Days to weeks</td>
            <td class="p-14">30 seconds</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Learning curve</td>
            <td class="p-14">Steep</td>
            <td class="p-14">Almost none</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Design control</td>
            <td class="p-14">Pixel-perfect</td>
            <td class="p-14">Limited editing</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">AI generation</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
            <td class="p-14">Full (site + content)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">CMS</td>
            <td class="p-14">Powerful built-in</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Ecommerce</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (advanced)</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Blogging</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (via CMS)</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">CRM</td>
            <td class="p-14">No (integration needed)</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (built-in)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Invoicing</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Code export</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes</td>
            <td class="p-14">No</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Custom domains</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (paid plans)</td>
            <td class="p-14">Yes (paid plans)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b bg-gray-50">
            <td class="p-4 font-bold">Starting price</td>
            <td class="p-14">$14/month</td>
            <td class="p-14">$15/month</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Pricing Comparison
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Webflow Pricing</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Starter:</strong> Free (Webflow branding, limited)</li>
          <li>• <strong>Basic:</strong> $14/month or $12/month annually</li>
          <li>• <strong>CMS:</strong> $23/month or $16/month annually</li>
          <li>• <strong>Business:</strong> $39/month or $27/month annually (ecommerce)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Worth it for designers and agencies. Powerful CMS and ecommerce at Business tier.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Durable Pricing</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Starter:</strong> $15/month - Basic website</li>
          <li>• <strong>Business:</strong> $25/month - More features</li>
          <li>• <strong>Mogul:</strong> $80/month - Multiple sites</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Includes hosting, CRM, invoicing. All-in-one pricing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Webflow and Durable are completely different tools. Webflow is a powerful platform you learn. Durable is an AI service that generates for you.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Choose Webflow if you want:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• Complete design control (pixel-perfect)</li>
        <li>• To build complex sites (ecommerce, CMS)</li>
        <li>• Custom animations and interactions</li>
        <li>• To export code and host elsewhere</li>
        <li>• To invest time in learning a powerful tool</li>
        <li>• Career in design/development</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Choose Durable if you want:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• Complete website in 30 seconds</li>
        <li>• AI to generate content and design</li>
        <li>• Zero technical learning curve</li>
        <li>• Built-in business tools (CRM, invoicing)</li>
        <li>• To move on to running your business</li>
        <li>• Functional site fast, not custom design</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Both have free trials:</strong> Webflow lets you try free (with branding). Durable has free trial available. Try both. See which workflow fits your needs and timeline.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related Comparisons
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/webflow-vs-wordpress" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Webflow vs WordPress</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">No-code vs classic CMS</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/durable-vs-wordpress" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable vs WordPress</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI builder vs classic CMS</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
